Makefile which scales and converts jpg, tga and ppm files to png and generates an archive

VARIABLES
  SIZE     - specifies the largest image size (default=100)

TARGETS
  all      - default target, does the same as tar target
  archive  - scale and convert all jpg, tga and ppm files to png and create an archive.tgz
  png      - scale and convert all jpg, tga and ppm files to png
  help     - display this help and exit
  clean    - remove all generated files
